stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> LoginPage: User accesses login page
    
    LoginPage --> EmailInput: Display email input field
    
    EmailInput --> EmailValidation: User enters work email
    note right of EmailInput
        Single input field for
        work email address
    end note
    
    EmailValidation --> SendVerification: Email format valid
    EmailValidation --> EmailInput: Invalid email format
    
    SendVerification --> VerificationEmail: System sends secure email
    note right of SendVerification
        Generates unique,
        time-sensitive token
    end note
    
    VerificationEmail --> TokenValidation: User clicks link
    note right of VerificationEmail
        Contains encrypted
        verification link
    end note
    
    TokenValidation --> SessionCreation: Token valid
    TokenValidation --> LoginPage: Token expired/invalid
    
    SessionCreation --> Dashboard: Auto-login successful
    note right of SessionCreation
        Establishes secure session
        Sets role-based access
    end note
    
    Dashboard --> ActiveSession: Session monitoring
    
    ActiveSession --> SessionValidation: Continuous validation
    SessionValidation --> ActiveSession: Session valid
    SessionValidation --> LoginPage: Session timeout/invalid
    
    ActiveSession --> [*]: User logs out